### 3. CHECK DRIVER STATUS
GET {{baseUrl}}/verification/taxi/status
Authorization: {{token}}


### 4. ADMIN: APPROVE DRIVER APPLICATION
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/taxi/admin/approve-reject
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "decision": "approve"
}
# Note: 'reason' field is NOT needed for approval

### 5. ADMIN: REJECT DRIVER APPLICATION
POST {{baseUrl}}/verification/taxi/admin/approve-reject
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "decision": "reject",
  "reason": "Insurance certificate expired. Please upload current insurance valid for at least 6 months and re-apply."
}
# Note: 'reason' field is REQUIRED when rejecting (minimum 10 characters)

